  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><span dir=\"ltr\">This poison is best ingested, but can be applied to a weapon for less potency.</span></p><p><span dir=\"ltr\"> A creature whom ingests this poison must succeed a DC 20 Constitution saving throw, as the poison ignites the stomach acid within the creature taking 8d8 fire damage that ignores resistances on a failed saved, or half as much on a successful save.</span></p><p><span dir=\"ltr\"> The creature must succeed a DC 18 Constitution saving throw each round until they pass, ending this effect, taking 3d8 fire damage on a failed save.</span></p><p> </p><p><span dir=\"ltr\">Effective Rank: B-Rank</span></p><p><span dir=\"ltr\">Poison Craft DC: 26</span></p>",
